  VERSION="4.04.2"
 OVERSION="4.02"
 CATEGORY="graphic security"
ATTRIBUTE="gnome|x11"
      URL="http://www.jwz.org/xscreensaver"
      REQ="bc glut gtk+2 libxml2 netpbm zlib"
   OPT[0]="Linux-PAM:::"
   OPT[1]="audiofile:::for audio support"
   OPT[2]="esound:::for esd audio output"
   OPT[3]="control-center:::for gnome support"
    SHORT="xscreensaver is a modular screen saver and locker for X Windows."
cat << EOF
XScreenSaver is a modular screen saver and locker for the X Window
System.  It is highly customizable and allows the use of any program
that can draw on the root window as a display mode.  More than 120
display modes are included in this package.
EOF
